DESCRIPTION:This post contains affiliate links. We earn a commission if you
	 purchase tickets through our links at no extra cost to you. \nOfficial Ti
	ckets\nResale Tickets \nMorgan Jay: The Goofy Guy Tour LIVE at Premier The
	ater at Foxwoods Resort Casino\nRising comedy star Morgan Jay brings his w
	ildly popular Goofy Guy Tour to the Premier Theater at Foxwoods Resort Cas
	ino in Mashantucket\, CT on July 2\, 2026. Known for his infectious energy
	\, relatable storytelling\, and hilarious crowd work\, Morgan Jay delivers
	 a comedy experience unlike any other. \nEvent Details\nDate: Thursday\, J
	uly 2\, 2026\nTime: 7:00 PM (Doors open 6:00 PM)\nVenue: Premier Theater a
	t Foxwoods Resort Casino\nAddress: 39 Norwich Westerly Road\, Mashantucket
	\, CT 06339\nAge Requirement: 16 & Over\nTicket Prices: Starting at $34 \n
	About Morgan Jay\nMorgan Jay is a fast-rising comedian who has taken the c
	omedy world by storm with his viral videos\, sold-out tours\, and Netflix 
	appearances. His debut feature film premiered at SXSW 2025 in the Narrativ
	e Spotlight section\, cementing his status as one of comedy’s brightest ne
	w stars. His Goofy Guy Tour has been selling out venues across the country
	. \nWhat to Expect\n\nHigh-energy stand-up comedy performance\nHilarious c
	rowd interaction and improvisation\nRelatable storytelling and observation
	al humor\n16+ event at a world-class casino resort venue\nOne of comedy’s 
	hottest rising stars live on stage\nUnforgettable night of laughs at Foxwo
	ods\n\nVenue Information\nThe Premier Theater at Foxwoods Resort Casino is
	 a state-of-the-art entertainment venue located at 39 Norwich Westerly Roa
	d in Mashantucket\, CT. The theater offers excellent sightlines\, premium 
	seating\, and all the amenities of the world-famous Foxwoods Resort Casino
	 complex. \nTicket Information\nTickets start at $34 and are available now
	. This is a 16+ event. All ticket sales are final and non-refundable. Purc
	hase official tickets through Ticketmaster or find resale tickets on Vivid
	Seats. \nOfficial Tickets\nResale Tickets \nThis post contains affiliate l
	inks. We earn a commission if you purchase tickets through our links at no
	 extra cost to you.\nAll sales are final. Show times subject to change. Va
	lid photo ID may be required for entry.\n\nhttps://comedycalendar.com/even
	t/morgan-jay-the-goofy-guy-tour-live-at-premier-theater-at-foxwoods-resort
	-casino/\n\nFrom Comedy Calendar
URL:https://comedycalendar.com/event/morgan-jay-the-goofy-guy-tour-live-at-
	premier-theater-at-foxwoods-resort-casino/
LOCATION:Premier Theater at Foxwoods Resort Casino\, 39 Norwich Westerly Ro
	ad\, Mashantucket\, CT\, 6339\, United States Of America
