SUMMARY:DeRay Davis LIVE at The Theater at MGM National Harbor
DTSTAMP:20260701T101458Z
DTSTART:20260703T200000Z
DESCRIPTION:This post contains affiliate links. We earn a commission if you
	 purchase tickets through our links at no extra cost to you. \nOfficial Ti
	ckets\nResale Tickets \nDeRay Davis LIVE at The Theater at MGM National Ha
	rbor\nDeRay Davis\, one of comedy’s most electrifying performers\, brings 
	his high-energy stand-up show to The Theater at MGM National Harbor in Nat
	ional Harbor\, Maryland for a special July 4th weekend performance. Known 
	for his explosive delivery and hilarious storytelling\, DeRay is set to de
	liver a night of non-stop laughs. \nEvent Details\nDate: Friday\, July 3\,
	 2026\nTime: 8:00 PM\nVenue: The Theater at MGM National Harbor\nAddress: 
	101 MGM National Ave\, National Harbor\, MD 20745\nAge Requirement: 18+ (v
	alid photo ID required) \nAbout DeRay Davis\nDeRay Davis is a Chicago-born
	 stand-up comedian and actor best known for his roles in films like 21 Jum
	p Street and Barbershop\, as well as his appearances on Wild ‘N Out. With 
	a style that blends sharp observational humor with raw street comedy\, DeR
	ay has built a massive following through his Netflix specials and sold-out
	 live shows across the country. \nWhat to Expect\n\nHigh-energy stand-up c
	omedy from one of the game’s best\nHilarious stories drawn from real life 
	and pop culture\nA perfect July 4th weekend night out in the DC/Maryland a
	rea\nWorld-class venue with excellent sightlines and sound\nAn unforgettab
	le evening of laughs at MGM National Harbor\n\nVenue Information\nThe Thea
	ter at MGM National Harbor is a premier entertainment venue located just m
	inutes from Washington\, DC\, offering state-of-the-art acoustics\, comfor
	table seating\, and a full casino resort experience. The venue hosts top-t
	ier comedy\, music\, and entertainment acts year-round. \nTicket Informati
	on\nTickets are available now through Ticketmaster (official) and VividSea
	ts (resale). Secure your seats early as this show is expected to sell out 
	for the holiday weekend. \nOfficial Tickets\nResale Tickets \nThis post co
	ntains affiliate links. We earn a commission if you purchase tickets throu
	gh our links at no extra cost to you.\nAll sales are final. Show times sub
	ject to change. Valid photo ID may be required for entry.\n\nhttps://comed
	ycalendar.com/event/deray-davis-live-at-the-theater-at-mgm-national-harbor
	/\n\nFrom Comedy Calendar
URL:https://comedycalendar.com/event/deray-davis-live-at-the-theater-at-mgm
	-national-harbor/
LOCATION:The Theater at MGM National Harbor\, 101 MGM National Ave\, Nation
	al Harbor\, MD\, 20745\, United States
