	 5\, 2026\nTime: 7:00 PM\nVenue: OLG Stage at Fallsview Casino\nAddress: 6
	366 Stanley Ave\, Niagara Falls\, ON L2G 3Y5 \nAbout “Weird Al” Yankovic\n
	“Weird Al” Yankovic is the best-selling comedy recording artist of all tim
	e\, with 5 Grammy Awards and over 12 million albums sold. Known for his hi
	larious parodies of pop songs and original comedy compositions\, Weird Al 
	has been entertaining audiences for over four decades. \nWhat to Expect\n\
	nA spectacular live show featuring decades of comedy hits\nHilarious parod
	ies and original comedy songs\nElaborate costumes and high-energy performa
	nces\nA world-class venue experience at Fallsview Casino\nAn unforgettable
	 night of comedy and music\n\nVenue Information\nThe OLG Stage at Fallsvie
	w Casino is a premier entertainment venue at 6366 Stanley Ave in Niagara F
	alls\, Ontario. \nTicket Information\nTickets start at $90. Get your seats
