 n.org/wp-content/uploads/2026/05/IMG_4987.jpeg
ATTACH;FMTTYPE=image/jpeg:https://www.levyparkhouston.org/wp-content/upload
 s/2026/05/IMG_4987.jpeg
UID:wLQowUd1vUJGp8rjbSi7I
SUMMARY:Free Watch Party: Quarterfinals Day 1
DTSTAMP:20260701T101458Z
DTSTART:20260709T133000Z
DESCRIPTION:The group stage drama is behind us — now it’s pure knockout soc
	cer. Eight teams left standing\, and tonight two of them go to war for a s
	pot in the semifinals. Come feel the electricity. \nKickoff is at 3:00 p.m
	. Admission is free! \nCommunity Partners: Further enhancing programming\,
	 Levy Park will partner with local organizations to broaden community enga
	gement\, including collaborations with cultural groups and soccer-focused 
	nonprofits. Levy Park is seeking enthusiastic volunteers and community par
	tner organizations to help bring this festival to life. Volunteers will wo
	rk directly alongside our event team\, supporting booth operations and hel
	ping ensure every guest has an unforgettable experience. Email us to learn
	 more about volunteer opportunities. \nFood and Beverage Concessions: Enjo
	y a variety of festival food fare\, beer and wine\, and non-alcoholic beve
	rages from Coca-Cola. \nMerchandise: Event merchandise celebrating Houston
	\, Levy Park\, and the global soccer tournament will also be available for
	 purchase. \nArt Installations and Photo Opportunities: Commemorate the ex
	perience with a photo tour of the park\, including life-sized soccer-theme
	d photo backdrops and a tournament bracket. Visit our soccer ball music bo
	x and turn the crank for festive sounds.\n\nhttps://www.levyparkhouston.or
	g/events/quarterfinals-day-1/\n\nFrom Levy Park Houston
URL:https://www.levyparkhouston.org/events/quarterfinals-day-1/
X-CALRIPPER-SOURCE:levy-park-houston
CATEGORIES:Levy Park Houston
TRANSP:TRANSPARENT
DURATION:PT5H
END:VEVENT
