SUMMARY:Sunset Bingo at Levy Park
DTSTAMP:20260701T101458Z
DTSTART:20260710T180000Z
DESCRIPTION:Bring your crew the second Friday of each month for a fun eveni
	ng where you can take home fantastic prizes. Set to the backdrop of soulfu
	l tunes from DJ Del Sur\, Sunset Bingo is a great way to unwind and suppor
	t Levy Park. All event proceeds directly support the park’s operations and
	 programming. Please note: While children (and pups) can play\, an adult (
	18+) must be present to claim a prize. \n$10 for 8 games\; $1 daubers are 
	available for purchase\, or BYODauber (bring your own dauber). CASH ONLY \
	nEvent Schedule:\n6 p.m. – Board Sales Begin\n7 p.m. – Games Begin \nFood 
	& Beverage Concessions: Enjoy convenient counter service with easy-to-eat\
	, handheld favorites like tortas\, flautas\, hot dogs\, and tacos at Gaspa
	chos Mexican Bites—plus special treats for your four-legged friends! Hears
	ay is also serving up its eclectic cuisine\, refreshing cocktails\, and tr
	eats for your pup. Kind Ice Cream offers a 10% discount during games\, all
	owing Bingo participants to enjoy its irresistible selection of cakes and 
	ice cream treats. Outside alcohol is not permitted but may be purchased fr
	om park concessionaires. \nNo outside furniture is allowed. Park furniture
	 will be available\, or guests may bring a blanket for lawn seating. \nPar
	king\nParking is available adjacent to the park and along Eastside Street 
	and Wakeforest Avenue. Additional public parking (parking rate applies) is
	 available in the Kirby Grove parking garage located on the corner of Rich
	mond and Wakeforest. \nPlease note: Prizes and sponsors may vary by event.
	 If you would like to donate an in-kind prize or sponsor Sunset Bingo\, pl
	ease contact us at info@levyparkhouston.org. \n \n\nhttps://www.levyparkho
	uston.org/events/sunset-bingo-at-levy-park/\n\nFrom Levy Park Houston
URL:https://www.levyparkhouston.org/events/sunset-bingo-at-levy-park/
X-CALRIPPER-SOURCE:levy-park-houston
CATEGORIES:Levy Park Houston
TRANSP:TRANSPARENT
DURATION:PT3H
END:VEVENT
