SUMMARY:Summer Film: Hill “Halfon” Doesn’t Answer
DTSTAMP:20260701T101459Z
DTSTART:20260716T193000Z
DESCRIPTION:Hill “Halfon” Doesn’t Answer Directed by Asi Dayan (1976)  \nCo
	medy | 92 Minutes | Hebrew with English subtitles \nJoin us for the celebr
	ation of the 50th anniversary of the legendary film which became the great
	est cult film in the history of Israeli cinema. In this satirical cult-cla
	ssic\, a reserve unit in the Israel-controlled Sinai is less than five mil
	es from the Egyptian front lines. However\, the Israelis are hardly concer
	ned with the Egyptians\, as half of the Reserve-niks are just happy to get
	 away from their homes and essentially go camping in uniform\, while the o
	ther half goes crazy in hilarious fashion.\n\nhttps://www.erjcchouston.org
	/event/summer-film-hill-halfon-doesnt-answer/\n\nFrom ERJCC Houston
URL:https://www.erjcchouston.org/event/summer-film-hill-halfon-doesnt-answe
	r/
LOCATION:Kaplan Theatre @ the J\, 5601 S. Braeswood\, Houston\, TX\, 77096
X-CALRIPPER-SOURCE:erjcc-houston
CATEGORIES:ERJCC Houston
TRANSP:TRANSPARENT
DURATION:PT1H
END:VEVENT
