BEGIN:VEVENT
IMAGE;VALUE=URI;DISPLAY=BADGE;FMTTYPE=image/png:https://houstonarboretum.or
 g/wp-content/uploads/2026/05/Phenology-1280-x-720.png
ATTACH;FMTTYPE=image/png:https://houstonarboretum.org/wp-content/uploads/20
 26/05/Phenology-1280-x-720.png
UID:yxmnZyk3_3dLjfBJYTpYX
SUMMARY:Fourth Saturday Phenology Walk
DTSTAMP:20260701T101459Z
DTSTART:20260725T090000Z
DESCRIPTION:Fourth Saturday of the Month9:00 – 11:00 amFree\, donations app
	reciatedAll ages\, minors must be accompanied by an adult \n\n\n\nMeet in 
	front of the Nature Center building \n\n\n\nDiscover the hidden seasonal r
	hythms of nature firsthand on our guided Phenology Walks\, where we track 
	the life cycles of different plants across ecosystems\, from the first spr
	ing bud burst to winter dormancy. You’ll learn how shifting weather patter
	ns and climate change influence the timing of these important events in ou
	r local ecosystems and how you can become a community scientist\, contribu
	ting vital data from your own backyard to a global research initiative.  \
	n\n\n\nThese relaxing morning walks are led by scientists from Rice Univer
	sity and staff from the Arboretum. We welcome nature enthusiasts of all ag
	es\, however kids 12 years and younger must be accompanied by a guardian. 
	\n\n\n\nLearn more about the study of phenology and ways you can contribut
	e at https://www.usanpn.org/nn \n\n\n\n\n\n\n\nCommunity Science Partner\n
	\nhttps://houstonarboretum.org/event/fourth-saturday-phenology-walk/2026-0
	7-25/\n\nFrom Houston Arboretum & Nature Center
URL:https://houstonarboretum.org/event/fourth-saturday-phenology-walk/2026-
	07-25/
X-CALRIPPER-SOURCE:houston-arboretum
CATEGORIES:Houston Arboretum & Nature Center
TRANSP:TRANSPARENT
DURATION:PT2H
END:VEVENT
BEGIN:VEVENT
IMAGE;VALUE=URI;DISPLAY=BADGE;FMTTYPE=image/png:https://ccs-houston.com/wp-
 content/uploads/2026/05/Event-Launch-Kit-Houston-World-of-Hot-Wheels-IV.pn
 g
ATTACH;FMTTYPE=image/png:https://ccs-houston.com/wp-content/uploads/2026/05
 /Event-Launch-Kit-Houston-World-of-Hot-Wheels-IV.png
UID:lRcp2iwh1cye9aFLpOoaU
SUMMARY:Houston World of Hot Wheels IV
DTSTAMP:20260701T101459Z
DTSTART:20260725T100000Z
DESCRIPTION:🚗🏁 Houston World of Hot Wheels IV is roaring back with more thr
	ills and speed! 🏁🚗\nAfter an electric\, action-packed weekend of nonstop d
	eals\, racing\, and collector excitement\, Houston World of Hot Wheels IV 
	is revving up for another round! We’re bringing even MORE vendors\, MORE c
	ars\, and MORE action for collectors\, racers\, and families to enjoy all 
	weekend long. ⚡ \n  \n📅 July 25–26\, 2026 | 10AM–5PM\n📍 9700 Bissonnet St 
	1500\, Houston\, TX\n🎟️ FREE Entry + FREE Parking \n  \nEvent Highlights\n🛒
	 Hot Wheels Swap & Shop – Both Days \n50+ vendors. 30\,000+ Hot Wheels\, M
	atchbox\, and diecast to dig through. STHs\, TH variations\, premium Car C
	ulture\, redline-era pieces\, MOC vintage\, loose mainline bins\, M2s\, Gr
	eenlights\, Johnny Lightnings. Bring your want list! \n  \n🚗✨ Houston Diec
	ast Custom Contest – 10AM-3PM | Both Days \nCalling all builders and custo
	m kings 👑 Bring your best custom Hot Wheels/Matchbox build — paint\, wheel
	 swaps\, stance\, body kits\, full one-of-one creations. This contest is f
	or the detail freaks and the true “trust the process” customizers. 🏆 The w
	inner will be announced at 4PM and will receive a prize sponsored by Domin
	go! ✨ Hosted by @funopolistoys \n  \n🏁 Hot Wheels Racing Contest – Both Da
	ys\nThe stage track is live all weekend. Hourly races\, prizes for winners
	\, FREE to enter. \n  \n🏎️ Car Show (Parking Lot Showcase) \nTake it outsid
	e and check out Houston’s coolest real-life rides. Style\, horsepower\, an
	d car-community energy all in one spot. \n  \n👶 Mini Zones & Family Fun\nF
	un spaces for younger collectors and first‑time racers — all ages welcome!
	 \n  \n🚨 VENDORS WANTED\nGot STHs\, vintage redlines\, custom builds\, or 
	bulk mainline to move? This is your crowd.\n📥 Apply: https://tinyurl.com/C
	CSGuestVendorFromHouston \n  \n🏨 Special Hotel Deals\nEnjoy a special room
	 rate of $79/night at TownePlace Suites\, just about 15 minutes from the v
	enue!\n👉 Book: https://www.marriott.com/event-reservations/reservation-lin
	k.mi?id=1767823967549&key=CORP&app=resvlink \n  \nHunt or race. Trade or j
	ust walk the floor. The customs will be parked outside\, the bins will be 
	open inside\, and the track will be running all weekend. See you July 25–2
	6.\n\nhttps://ccs-houston.com/events/houston-world-of-hot-wheels-iv/\n\nFr
	om CCS Houston
URL:https://ccs-houston.com/events/houston-world-of-hot-wheels-iv/
X-CALRIPPER-SOURCE:ccs-houston
CATEGORIES:CCS Houston
TRANSP:TRANSPARENT
DURATION:PT31H
END:VEVENT
