 s/2026/06/HRW2026-1200x900-2.jpg
UID:Mhe1hFakus0EejKyj_FkR
SUMMARY:Houston Restaurant Weeks 2026
DTSTAMP:20260701T101459Z
DTSTART:20260801T000000Z
DESCRIPTION:Houston Restaurant Weeks is the largest annual fundraiser for A
	merica’s largest food bank\, the Houston Food Bank. It’s a month-long dini
	ng extravaganza featuring specially priced lunches\, brunches\, and dinner
	s at restaurants from The Woodlands to Galveston. \nParticipating restaura
	nts make donations based on how many prix fixe brunches\, lunches\, and di
	nners they sell during the event. Diners are not solicited for donations. 
	\nBeginning July 15\, diners can visit HoustonRestaurantWeeks.com to view 
	the 2026 list of restaurants that have committed to participate\, along wi
	th their HRW menus. \nThe event includes restaurants located in Harris\, G
	alveston\, and Montgomery counties. The Galveston County Food Bank and Mon
	tgomery County Food Bank are part of the Houston Food Bank’s Affiliate Foo
	d Banks. The Houston Food Bank provides food to these smaller food banks\,
	 which in turn distribute the food to hunger relief charities in a portion
	 of HFB’s service area. The Houston Food Bank certifies that their Affilia
	te Food Banks meet Feeding America standards.\n\nhttps://www.houstonfoodba
	nk.org/upcomingevent/houston-restaurant-weeks-2026/\n\nFrom Houston Food B
	ank
URL:https://www.houstonfoodbank.org/upcomingevent/houston-restaurant-weeks-
	2026/
X-CALRIPPER-SOURCE:houston-food-bank
CATEGORIES:Houston Food Bank
TRANSP:TRANSPARENT
DURATION:PT912H
END:VEVENT
