SUMMARY:CCS $20\,000 cEDH Invitational Qualifier #3
DTSTAMP:20260701T101459Z
DTSTART:20260801T090000Z
DESCRIPTION:🏆 CCS $20\,000 cEDH Invitational Qualifier #3 🏆\nThe race tight
	ens. The margins shrink. \nQualifier #3 brings us into the mid season of t
	he CCS $50\,000 cEDH Invitational Series. With only three events after\, e
	very decision matters and every point is gold. \nFull Details → https://to
	pdeck.gg/event/ccs-50000-cedh-invitational \n  \n🗓 Dates: August 1–2\, 202
	6 \n📍 Location: Charlie’s Collectible Show\, 9700 Bissonett St Unit 1500\,
	 Houston\, TX 77036 \n\nTournament Details:\n\n🎟️ Entry Fee: $90 before Jul
	y 18\, $110 After\n🔗 Register Now! 👉  https://topdeck.gg/event/css-20000-c
	edh-invitational-qualifier-4\n\n🗂️ Format & Structure\n\nFormat: cEDH (Prox
	y Friendly)\nSaturday: 6 Swiss Rounds (based on attendance)\nSunday: 2 Swi
	ss Rounds → Top 16\n\n🚫 Proxy Requirements: \n\nFull card name\, mana cost
	\, type line\, and effect text\nTest cards or clearly written MDFCs allowe
	d\nNo paper slip-ins permitted\n\n💰 Guaranteed $20\,000 Prize Pool\n\n1st 
	— $5\,000 + Auto Invite + TopDeck Invite + 200 pts\n2nd-4th — $2\,000 each
	 + Auto Invite + 160 pts\n5th–8th — $550 + 120 pts\n9th–16th — $550 + 100 
	pts\n17th–32nd — $175 + 75 pts\n33rd–48th — 60 pts\n49th–64th — 45 pts\n65
	th–96th — 30 pts\n97th–128th — 20 pts\n\nEvent Schedule:\n🕔 Registration O
	pens: 9 AM \n🕔 Player Meeting (Day 1): 10 AM \n🕔 Day 2 Start Time: 9 AM \n
	🛍️ Collectible Marketplace\nBetween rounds\, enjoy access to a curated mark
	etplace featuring: \n\nTCG singles\, sealed\, and accessories\nRetro video
	 games & consoles\nAnime merch\, figures\, and models\nToys and other hobb
	y collectibles\n\nPerfect for grabbing upgrades\, browsing grails\, or jus
	t hanging out between matches. \n🏨 Special Hotel Deals\nEnjoy a special ra
	te of $79/night — 2 Queens at TownePlace Suites\, only 15 minutes distance
	 from the action! \nBook your stay 👉🏻 https://www.marriott.com/event-reserv
	ations/reservation-link.mi?id=1767823967549&key=CORP&app=resvlink \n🔔 IMPO
	RTANT REMINDERS\n\nPlayer names will appear as real names on published doc
	uments.\nTop 16 decklists will be published.\n\n🔥 Late-season stakes hit h
	ard — tighten your game and push forward. Your run to the $50K Invitationa
	l continues at CCS cEDH Qualifier #3!\n\nhttps://ccs-houston.com/events/cc
	s-20000-cedh-invitational-qualifier-3/\n\nFrom CCS Houston
URL:https://ccs-houston.com/events/ccs-20000-cedh-invitational-qualifier-3/
X-CALRIPPER-SOURCE:ccs-houston
CATEGORIES:CCS Houston
TRANSP:TRANSPARENT
DURATION:PT33H
END:VEVENT
