BEGIN:VEVENT
IMAGE;VALUE=URI;DISPLAY=BADGE;FMTTYPE=image/png:https://ccs-houston.com/wp-
 content/uploads/2026/06/Event-Launch-Kit-Houston-Toy-Exchange-III.png
ATTACH;FMTTYPE=image/png:https://ccs-houston.com/wp-content/uploads/2026/06
 /Event-Launch-Kit-Houston-Toy-Exchange-III.png
UID:l70yeSRS9r6lZ30QwxXjI
SUMMARY:Houston Toy Exchange III
DTSTAMP:20260701T101459Z
DTSTART:20260802T050000Z
DESCRIPTION:Houston Toy Exchange III — The Floor Is Loaded\, Houston\nSomew
	here on this floor is the piece you have been hunting for months. 🔥 \nHous
	ton Toy Exchange III is a pure toy marketplace\, no convention noise\, no 
	filler. Just collectors\, families\, and dealers moving action figures\, v
	intage finds\, and modern grails across one packed floor at CCS Houston. T
	he fun is in the hunt: digging through a bin you have never seen\, talking
	 shop with someone who knows the line better than you do\, and walking out
	 with something you did not expect to find. \n  \n📅 Date: Sunday\, August 
	2\, 2026 | 10AM – 5PM \n📍 Location: 9700 Bissonnet St\, #1500\, Houston\, 
	TX 77036 \n🎟️ FREE Entry + FREE Parking \n  \n🔥 What You’ll Find on the Flo
	or 🔥 \n🛍️ Toy Marketplace Tables packed with action figures\, vintage toys\
	, sealed and loose\, nostalgia pieces\, and the modern lines collectors ar
	e actually chasing right now. Every table is its own dig. Come search the 
	floor. \n  \n💰 Buy\, Sell\, Trade Bring the toys you are ready to pass alo
	ng or trade up for something you have been chasing. Collectors and vendors
	 are buying\, selling\, and trading all day. Connect\, negotiate\, and kee
	p great pieces moving through the community. \n  \n🔍 Toy Appraisals Holdin
	g something and not sure what it’s worth? One of our experienced vendors i
	s running toy appraisals all day\, sharing insights on value\, rarity\, an
	d trade potential so you can make confident\, informed deals on the floor.
	 \n  \n🧩 Toy Scavenger Hunt Challenge Turn the hunt into a game. Work the 
	marketplace and complete the Toy Hunt Challenge by tracking down specific 
	toy categories across multiple booths for a shot at prizes and collector b
	ragging rights. \n  \n📸 Toy Flex Wall Score something special? Show it off
	. Snap a photo of your best pickup at the Toy Flex Wall and share your fin
	d with the community. \n  \nLongtime collector or just starting out\, Hous
	ton Toy Exchange III is about connecting\, swapping stories\, and keeping 
	the love of toys alive together. Bring your toys\, bring your curiosity\, 
	pull up. \n  \nWant in as a vendor? Tables are open: https://tinyurl.com/C
	CSGuestVendorFromHouston \n  \nHouston Toy Exchange III. Bring your toys\,
	 bring your curiosity\, and come move some pieces.\n\nhttps://ccs-houston.
	com/events/houston-toy-exchange-iii/\n\nFrom CCS Houston
URL:https://ccs-houston.com/events/houston-toy-exchange-iii/
X-CALRIPPER-SOURCE:ccs-houston
CATEGORIES:CCS Houston
TRANSP:TRANSPARENT
DURATION:PT17H
END:VEVENT
