BEGIN:VEVENT
IMAGE;VALUE=URI;DISPLAY=BADGE;FMTTYPE=image/jpeg:https://houstonarboretum.o
 rg/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/Tiny-Trekkers-Little-Explorers-Arboretum-Sta
 ff.jpg
ATTACH;FMTTYPE=image/jpeg:https://houstonarboretum.org/wp-content/uploads/2
 024/02/Tiny-Trekkers-Little-Explorers-Arboretum-Staff.jpg
UID:xCYygvOMgmR8epIt2BmTq
SUMMARY:Little Explorers
DTSTAMP:20260701T101459Z
DTSTART:20260806T093000Z
DESCRIPTION:Thursday June 4 – Aug 69:30 – 10:30 am11:00 am – 12:00 pm \n\n\
	n\n$10 member / $12 nonmember (per child\, per class)Ages 2-4 \n\n\n\nEach
	 child must be accompanied by their guardian. Siblings are welcome to atte
	nd but must be registered to participate. \n\n\n\nFamily Tree Membership a
	nd above required for member discount. \n\n\n\nOur youngest naturalists ar
	e invited to join us for hands-on nature exploration. This program is a pe
	rfect way for our Little Explorers to discover more about the natural worl
	d around them.  \n\n\n\nPlease come dressed for the outdoors\, including c
	losed-toe shoes. A parent or guardian is required to attend program with c
	hildren. \n\n\n\nSummer Children’s Program registration will open Tuesday\
	, February 3\, 2026 for Arboretum Members. Nonmember registration will ope
	n Tuesday\, February 10\, 2026. \n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n9:30 am Classes\n\n\n\
	n\n\n\n\n\nJune 4 – 9:30 am\n\n\n\n\n\nJune 11 – 9:30 am\n\n\n\n\n\nJune 1
	8 – 9:30 am\n\n\n\n\n\nJune 25 – 9:30 am\n\n\n\n\n\nJUly 2 – 9:30 am\n\n\n
