SUMMARY:Unified Topgolf Pro-Am (Houston-Katy)
DTSTAMP:20260701T101500Z
DTSTART:20260918T100000Z
DESCRIPTION:The Unified Topgolf Pro-Am is one of the most exciting and mean
	ingful community partnership events hosted by Special Olympics Texas\, bri
	nging together athletes\, families\, coaches\, volunteers\, corporate part
	ners\, and local business leaders for an unforgettable day of golf\, laugh
	ter\, connection\, and community impact. \nEach bay includes a Special Oly
	mpics Texas athlete paired alongside five golfers\, creating a truly uniqu
	e experience where relationships\, memories\, and meaningful moments are b
	uilt throughout the day. From friendly competition and team spirit to incr
	edible conversations and shared experiences\, the event is designed to bri
	ng people together in a fun and welcoming environment while directly suppo
	rting local athletes and programs. \nProceeds from the Unified Topgolf Pro
	-Am help provide year-round sports training\, competitions\, health initia
	tives\, leadership development\, and educational opportunities for childre
	n\, teenagers\, and adults with intellectual disabilities throughout the g
	reater Houston area. As the event continues growing each year\, the Unifie
	d Topgolf Pro-Am has quickly become a tremendous opportunity for organizat
	ions and community members to make a real impact while being part of somet
	hing incredibly energetic\, uplifting\, and memorable. \nFor more informat
	ion regarding sponsorship opportunities\, team entries\, volunteer involve
	ment\, or sponsorship opportunities\, please reach out to Jared Kossover\,
	 Strategic Partnerships Manager with Special Olympics Texas \nJared Kossov
	er \nE: jkossover@sotx.org \nC: 737-867-9659\n\nhttps://energycorridor.org
	/event/unified-topgolf-pro-am-houston-katy/2026-09-18/2/\n\nFrom Energy Co
	rridor Farmers Market
URL:https://energycorridor.org/event/unified-topgolf-pro-am-houston-katy/20
	26-09-18/2/
LOCATION:Topgolf-Katy\, 1030 Memorial Brook Blvd\, Houston\, TX 77084\, Hou
	ston\, 77084
X-CALRIPPER-SOURCE:energy-corridor-farmers-market
CATEGORIES:Energy Corridor Farmers Market
TRANSP:TRANSPARENT
DURATION:PT3H
END:VEVENT
